track_notes:
In my opinion this is the most easy access to the S5/BI-078 Summit. The last 5-10 minutes is quite steep with a lot of roots from the trees. But nothing special. I made it in 33 minutes. The peak is open enough for antennas. VHF/UHF is blocked by higher hills but still possible for those 4 QSO. Try to have HF with you.
73, Aleksander, S57S 12. NOV 2024
track_title: S57S Track from Litija. Free parking in the forest. Easy one.
